Notes: Championship Game of the Morgan Stanley (Easton office) Tip-off Tournament.
Avis Benjamin named to All-Tournament Team for Stevens Tech.
Sr. Alexiah Grant named Tournament Most Valuable Player for DeSales. Srs. Meg
Gallagher and Sondrine Glovas also named to All-Tournament Team.
Game.Officials: Karen Pammer,  Tom Blackwell,  Rick Fertig
